query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 1 AND q1.score <= 10
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('acceleration',
'astronomy',
'banach-algebras',
'c-star-algebras',
'coding-theory',
'computational-geometry',
'electricity',
'fibonacci-numbers',
'noncommutative-algebra',
'ordinals',
'projective-geometry',
'resource-recommendations',
'spectral-theory',
'speed-of-light',
'trees')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math',
'mathoverflow',
'physics')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
